    <!-- Help dialogs -->
    <string name="help_universal_mode">This is the universal-mode. You can turn off any TV by pointing your phone at the TV and pressing the red button. When the button is pressed, your phone will transmit a variety of IR-patterns from different brands to the TV, which should turn the TV off.</string>
    <string name="help_repetitive_mode">This mode works just like the universal-mode, only that your phone will transmit the IR-patterns over and over again once you have pressed the button. It will also continue to transmit when you close the application or lock your phone\'s screen. To stop repetitive-mode, just press the button a second time.</string>
    <string name="help_individual_mode">You can turn off TVs from specific brands here.</string>
